Detailed Description

Docking Station starter family description block.

The fields in a DFAM block are identical to those in a DSEX block so this class simply extends DSEXBlock.

Instantiates a new DFAMBlock.

If $prayfile is not null, all the data for this block will be read from the PRAYFile.

Parameters:
$prayfile The PRAYFile that this DFAM block belongs to.
$name The block's name.
$content The binary data of this block. May be null.
$flags The block's flags
